"NO" Motormaster states, "We need to return to base, but first, unhhhh" he
strains, "I want to partake in an ancient cybertronian pact. We are allies
of battle" with that he strainfully takes and odd shaped can from his chest
component and places it on the ground of Astroblast, he thens grabs what is
left of his left arm and opens a pipe in it. Fuel gushes out into the can.
He looks to Killfest, waiting for him to do the same.
